  "prompt": "What are the best Hindi songs to sing?",
  "response": "The choice of Hindi songs to sing can depend on your vocal range, personal taste, and the occasion. Here are some popular and well-loved Hindi songs that are often considered great for singing:\n\n### Classic Hits\n1. **\"Tum Hi Ho\" - Arijit Singh**\n2. **\"Kabira\" - Amaal Mallik & Tochi Raina**\n3. **\"Lag Ja Gale\" - Lata Mangeshkar**\n4. **\"Pehla Nasha\" - Udit Narayan & Sadhana Sargam**\n5. **\"Mere Mehboob Qayamat Hogi\" - Kishore Kumar**\n\n### Romantic Songs\n1. **\"Tera Ban Jaunga\" - Akhil Sachdeva & Tulsi Kumar**\n2. **\"Raabta\" - Arijit Singh**\n3. **\"Tujhse Naraz Nahi Zindagi\" - Anup Ghoshal**\n4. **\"Sun Saathiya\" - Priya Saraiya & Divya Kumar**\n5. **\"Dil Diyan Gallan\" - Atif Aslam**\n\n### Energetic/Party Songs\n1. **\"Badtameez Dil\" - Vishal Dadlani & Shreya Ghoshal**\n2. **\"Kar Gayi Chull\" - Badshah**\n3. **\"Malhari\" - Vishal Dadlani**\n4. **\"Saudagar Sauda Kar\" - Asha Bhosle & Kishore Kumar**\n5. **\"Aankh Marey\" - Neha Kakkar, Mika Singh & Kumar Sanu**\n\n### Fun/Folk Songs\n1. **\"Chura Liya Hai Tumne\" - Asha Bhosle & Mohammed Rafi**\n2. **\"Kala Chashma\" - Amar Arshi, Badshah & Neha Kakkar**\n3. **\"Genda Phool\" - Pritam & Rekha Bhardwaj**\n4. **\"Bolo Ta Ra Ra\" - Remo Fernandes**\n5. **\"Navrai Majhi\" - Swanand Kirkire & Sunidhi Chauhan**\n\n### Soulful Songs\n1. **\"Tujhse Naraz Nahi Zindagi\" - Anup Ghoshal**\n2. **\"Channa Mereya\" - Arijit Singh**\n3. **\"Agar Tum Saath Ho\" - Alka Yagnik & Arijit Singh**\n4. **\"Tera Hone Laga Hoon\" - Atif Aslam & Alisha Chinai**\n5. **\"Jeene Laga Hoon\" - Atif Aslam & Shreya Ghoshal**\n\nThese songs cover a variety of themes and moods, making them enjoyable for singing in different settings\u2014whether you're at a family gathering, karaoke night, or just practicing on your own! Choose songs that resonate with you for the best experience.",
